dct_title_s: Map of Property owned by the City of Jersey City situated on the banks of the Hackensack River
dct_description_sm: Map shows properties along the Hackensack River belonging to the city of Jersey City. This map also shows a tributary of the Hackensack River within the property with boundary lines on Cherry lane and Duffield Avenue.
